                <note>Engels beantwortet Marx’ Brief vom 27. November 1867 (<ref target="B00451"><?oxy_comment_start author="lindenberg" timestamp="20190314T181107+0100" comment="Br. 441"?>Marx
                        an Engels, 27.11.1867</ref><?oxy_comment_end?>). Marx antwortete Engels am
                    29. November 1867
                        (<?oxy_comment_start author="lindenberg" timestamp="20190314T181135+0100" comment="Br. 446"?><ref target="B00456">Marx an Engels, 29.11.1867</ref><?oxy_comment_end?>).</note>
